y allocating stat points, tailoring your strengths to match your chosen playstyle.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2644580/extras/5ee2b1bf52f07945c402a46c459e63e0.poster.avif?t=1738346705\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2644580/extras/5ee2b1bf52f07945c402a46c459e63e0.webm?t=1738346705\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2644580/extras/5ee2b1bf52f07945c402a46c459e63e0.mp4?t=1738346705\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>After defeating a monster, the loot it drops has dynamic prices that change with each dungeon run. You can sell these items for gems, which you can then use to purchase potions, ingredients, or upgrade your weapons.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2644580/extras/82f7c1306e958baf7cd472f34174b1da.avif?t=1738346705\" width=600 height=338 /></span>",
